OL,3,CUsers feel 'notification fatigue' as
OL,4,Cnews apps send up to 50 alerts a day
OL,6,FUsers of smartphone news apps have
OL,7,Freported feeling an increase in
OL,8,F"notification fatigue" as some news
OL,9,Foutlets are found to send up to 50
OL,10,Fmobile alerts a day.
OL,12,FA study published by Reuters Institute
OL,13,Ffor the Study of Journalism found that
OL,14,F43% of people who don't get news
OL,15,Falerts say that they have now actively
OL,16,Fdisabled them as a result of the
OL,17,Fabundance of notifications.
