OL,3,CUsers feel 'notification fatigue' as
OL,4,Cnews apps send up to 50 alerts a day
OL,6,FMany people now rely on their
OL,7,Fsmartphones for news updates, with 18%
OL,8,Fof people in the UK receiving weekly
OL,9,Fnotifications from their downloaded
OL,10,Fnews apps.
OL,12,FHowever, news platforms are reportedly
OL,13,Fsending too many breaking news alerts,
OL,14,Fwhich in turn is overwhelming and
OL,15,Firritating users.
