OL,3,CUsers feel 'notification fatigue' as
OL,4,Cnews apps send up to 50 alerts a day
OL,6,FThe number of daily alerts varies by
OL,7,Fpublisher, however the top offender in
OL,8,Fthe UK is reported to be BBC News,
OL,9,Fwhich sends a weekly average of 8
OL,10,Falerts per day, with as many as 4
OL,11,Fmillion people receiving the
OL,12,Fnotification each time.
OL,14,FThe second most likely news source to
OL,15,Fspam UK users' phones is Sky News.
OL,17,FInternational outlets such as CNN
OL,18,FIndonesia and the Jerusalem Post
OL,19,Faveraged a staggering 50 notifications
OL,20,Fa day.
