OL,3,CUsers feel 'notification fatigue' as
OL,4,Cnews apps send up to 50 alerts a day
OL,6,FTo combat the issue, some restrictions
OL,7,Fare being placed on the amount of
OL,8,Falerts the applications can send each
OL,9,Fday, with The Times being capped at
OL,10,Ffour per day.
OL,12,FDespite this, users are still turning
OL,13,Ftowards silencing notifications in an
OL,14,Fattempt to keep their notifications
OL,15,Fbox clear from news, with almost 80%
OL,16,Fof respondents admitting that they
OL,17,Fcurrently do not receive any news
OL,18,Falerts on their phone.
