OL,3,CUsers feel 'notification fatigue' as
OL,4,Cnews apps send up to 50 alerts a day
OL,6,FWhile many app users report that this
OL,7,Fis as a result of the overwhelming
OL,8,Famount of alerts, others stated that
OL,9,Fthey turned to removing notifications
OL,10,Fdue to the negative nature of the news
OL,11,Fstories every day, which was affecting
OL,12,Ftheir emotional wellbeing.
OL,14,FThis criticism follows on the back of
OL,15,Fa general sense of dissatisfaction
OL,16,Fwith news outlets, with news avoidance
OL,17,Fbecoming an increasingly turned to
OL,18,Ftrend.
