OL,3,CUsers feel 'notification fatigue' as
OL,4,Cnews apps send up to 50 alerts a day
OL,6,FApple and Google have warned news
OL,7,Foutlets to stop sending so many
OL,8,Fnotifications as users become
OL,9,Fincreasingly frustrated, opening up
OL,10,Fdiscussions about what further
OL,11,Frestrictions could be implemented to
OL,12,Fcombat these concerns.
OL,14,FNick Newman, a journalist and digital
OL,15,Fstrategist who published the study,
OL,16,Ftold ITV News: "I think notification
OL,17,Ffatigue is a really good way of
OL,18,Flooking at it.
