OL,6,F"I think they just need to think much
OL,7,Fmore carefully about the alerts they
OL,8,Fsend. But also, up until now, alerts
OL,9,Fhave been a very blunt instrument.
OL,11,F"More of that kind of differentiation,
OL,12,Fmore personalisation, getting to know
OL,13,Fthe audiences better is likely to keep
OL,14,Fpeople ... engaged."
